title: Freddie Med - Privacy policy
content:
Freddie Med is not optimized for Internet Explorer.

For a better performance,
we strongly recommend using one of the following browsers:


  • Google Chrome

  • Mozilla Firefox

  • Microsoft Edge

  • Apple Safari
